name: StyleSheet
description: An object implementing the StyleSheet interface represents a single style sheet. CSS style sheets will further implement the more specialized CSSStyleSheet interface.

members.name: StyleSheet.disabled
members.description: Is a Boolean representing whether the current stylesheet has been applied or not.

members.name: StyleSheet.href
members.description: Returns a DOMString representing the location of the stylesheet.

members.name: StyleSheet.media
members.description: Returns a MediaList representing the intended destination medium for style information.

members.name: StyleSheet.ownerNode
members.description: Returns a Node associating this style sheet with the current document.

members.name: StyleSheet.parentStyleSheet
members.description: Returns a StyleSheet including this one, if any; returns null if there aren't any.

members.name: StyleSheet.title
members.description: Returns a DOMString representing the advisory title of the current style sheet.

members.name: StyleSheet.type
members.description: Returns a DOMString representing the style sheet language for this style sheet.
